name: Response Response (Mini-CD Edition)
description:
Two songs that perfectly represent what an experimental and uncompromising band Jane Bondage has become over the years, creating a unique mixture of Progressive Rock and Hardcore.

For those of you, who like to hold an actual record in their hands, we produced this Mini-CD Edition. Strictly limited to 100 pieces, after that they are gone forever.

name: Gestures (CD Edition)
description:
Our Debut EP, which we recorded entirely ourselves. The german Metal Hammer liked Gestures so much, they named it "Demo of the Month" in October 2010, a decision one can only comment by saying "It better fuckin' be !!!".

Including 4 Tracks and some fantastic artwork by the wonderful Silvia Aparecida Martins.
